genresAdvancedInfo.name: kashmiri hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Kashmiri hip hop is a fusion of traditional Kashmiri music with modern hip hop beats and lyrics. It often addresses social and political issues faced by the region, with artists using their platform to raise awareness and promote change. The genre has gained popularity among the youth in the Kashmir Valley.
